-{"id":"orch-go-1020","title":"Explicit --model and --backend flags should never be overridden by infrastructure escape hatch","description":"When spawning with explicit --model codex --backend opencode, the infrastructure escape hatch silently overrides to --backend claude --tmux. This makes model evaluation impossible. Fix: explicit flags should always win over auto-detection. The escape hatch should only apply when no --model or --backend flag is given.","repro":"orch spawn --bypass-triage --model codex --backend opencode feature-impl 'task' =\u003e Output: Infrastructure work detected - auto-applying escape hatch (--backend claude --tmux). Agent spawns on Claude instead of Codex.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-02-17T20:01:13.662184-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","updated_at":"2026-02-17T20:01:13.662184-08:00","labels":["area:spawn","triage:ready"]}
